    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Through long and intensive training you mastered Flow. Few people in this world can match your capabilities in this area.</p><p>Gain the following master feats: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.pKnX7MGZayqZui0Z]{Aerobatics Mastery}.</p><p><strong>Skill Potency</strong></p><p>At 9th level, you gain a +2 item bonus to Acrobatics checks involving @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.SkZAQRkLLkmBQNB9]{Escape}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.Qf1ylAbdVi1rkc8M]{Maneuver in Flight}. At 17th level, this bonus increases to +3.</p>",
